## <a id='loadbalancer-tkgi-api'></a>Step 2: Configure an External Load Balancer

To set up an external load balancer for the <%= vars.control_plane %>, configure the external load balancer to resolve to the domain name you entered in the **<%= vars.product_tile %>** tile > **<%= vars.control_plane %>** > **API Hostname (FQDN)**
using the following information:

  - IP address from [Retrieve <%= vars.control_plane %> Endpoint](#retrieve-tkgi-api)
  - Ports 8443 and 9021
  - HTTPS or TCP protocol

